node.text:
Here’s a behind these scenes look at our massive and visually spectacular sets in Hawaii that were built on thousands of acres of land and reservoir. 

No CGI, but built from scratch to achieve an authentic Amazonian feel and tapestry. 

An enormous cinematic creation designed to take you and your families on THE ADVENTURE OF A LIFETIME! 

We had the best time, so much fun and so will you! 

Enjoy JUNGLE CRUISE in theaters worldwide & on DISNEY+ THIS FRIDAY!!! 🚢💀🌴🐆 🗺 🥃🌍

node.title: Cool JUNGLE CRUISE history: in 1955 Walt Disney himself was the skipper 🥃

node.text:
No costar of mine has ever put in harder work ~ with more tenacity, stamina, charm and eloquence than this posh British bird, Emily Blunt. 

As a duo, we’re the hardest workers in the room, speaking to press all day, every day, all around the world 🌍💪🏾

And we also have the most fun….
whilst breaking out the Mana 
🥃😈

Enjoy this video as we happily steer this Disney train right off its rails
🚂💀🤣

Raise em up, you posh bird and mahalo for all the incredible work 🙏🏾🥃

JUNGLE CRUISE finally arrives in theaters worldwide and on Disney+ THIS FRIDAY!!! 

#OffTheRails 
#ItsAJungleDownThere 
#IllDrinkToThat

node.title: After doing 12 HOURS STRAIGHT of press ~ Em & I blame the @Teremana 😂😈🥃

node.text:
After 3 years in the making, it was with butterflies, with mana and with so much love and gratitude for every soul in the theater that came to celebrate this special moment with us - our official worldwide JUNGLE CRUISE premiere.
It was an incredible experience to share safely alongside the fans, the press and best of all the REAL Disneyland Jungle Cruise skippers right there under the stars at Disneyland.

And very cool to take Emily on her first ever ride of JUNGLE CRUISE 🚢 💀🌴🌍

This one’s for you, Walt…
we hope our film makes your spirit proud! 

Cheers 🥃✨
#JungleCruise

node.title: A peak backstage with Emily & I for our JUNGLE CRUISE premiere day ⭐️🥂

node.text:
For me, that “thing” is a sunrise workout that anchors my day and stacks the cards in my favor to win 🃏 🔑 

An empty room with one cardio machine that faces a bare wall - ain’t looking like much, but you’d be surprised how much noise I’m able to block out and mentally charge up for the day. 

Protect your “thing that allows you to do what you do” and stack that deck in your favor so you can win. 

And thank you to my @Disney partners for having my back by getting me what I need on our big global press junket for JUNGLE CRUISE. 

#protectthething 🔑⚓️☯️
#myladyBertha 💀🖤💦
@zoaenergy💥

I brought the main event MANA MOBILE & @Teremana and Rock Toast, but YOU brought the MANA ENERGY! 

The energy and excitement was electric yesterday at Downtown Disney! We of course had to do a Teremana toast 🥃🥃 to all of you and then Emily decided to offer cocktails and my infamous Rock french toast to everyone all day long - on me - FOR FREE 🤣🥃🍞

Thank you to everyone who came out with their families and friends. You guys are making the MANA MOBILE a MUST EXPERIENCE EVENT! 😊👊🏾

#MANAMOBILE
#NationalTequilaDay
#DowntownDISNEY 
@Teremana

• In ONE WEEK, enjoy our @sevenbucksprod documentary that follows the larger-than-life story of legendary Hollywood stuntman, Eddie Braun, as he attempts one of the most dangerous stunts of all time - the Snake River Canyon rocket jump. 
Ironically, this jump nearly killed Eddie’s childhood hero, Evel Knievel.

STREAMING on @DisneyPlus JULY 23rd. 

@crsh4csh
#DisneyPlus
#SevenBucksProds

node.text:
I knew many years ago, the opportunity for me to make BLACK ADAM would be a ONCE IN A CAREER EVENT. 

It has been my true honor to go shoulder to shoulder with over 1,000 brilliant and hungry crew of filmmakers and storytellers to bring the antihero known as, BLACK ADAM to life. 

This has been one for the ages and easily the hardest labor and toughest grind mentally and physically of my entire career. 

Worth. Every. Second. 

Love you all.
Thank you all. 
And I’ll see you down the road. 
Now go have some fun with that $10,000 🤣💰

The hierarchy of power in the DC UNIVERSE is changing. 

Black Adam⚡️
#themaninblack

node.title: Honored and proud to say that’s an official wrap on BLACK ADAM⚡️

node.text:
Here’s a behind these scenes look at our massive and visually spectacular sets in Hawaii that were built on thousands of acres of land and reservoir. 

No CGI, but built from scratch to achieve an authentic Amazonian feel and tapestry. 

An enormous cinematic creation designed to take you and your families on THE ADVENTURE OF A LIFETIME! 

We had the best time, so much fun and so will you! 

Enjoy JUNGLE CRUISE in theaters worldwide & on DISNEY+ THIS FRIDAY!!! 🚢💀🌴🐆 🗺 🥃🌍

A BIG #teremanatuesday shout to all our Mana Ohana loving their @teremana! 

Appreciate ALL the videos you guys send and THANK YOU for making Teremana the most delicious and RECORD BREAKING tequila in spirits history. 

#tequilaofthepeople 
#teremana 🥃

node.text:
*scroll left ⬅️👈🏾
Blown away by the massive crowds our @Teremana Tequila Mobile aka #ManaMobile drew at Downtown Disney 🏰🎢 🥃🥃🔥🔥🔥🔥

We serve the most delicious and freshest tacos, my infamous French Toast aka #RockToast and of course, the best Teremana cocktails you’ve ever had. 

Thank you to EVERYONE who came out with your own MANA and POSITIVE VIBES!!! 
It’s been a long time so it was beautiful to see so many smiling, happy faces 😊👊🏾

Our Mana Mobile is rolling coast to coast and yes, just like this past weekend - if I personally show up and surprise YOU then you KNOW all the Teremana cocktails and food is gonna be FREEEEEEEE!!! 

Love you guys and thanks for making our Mana Mobile a DELICIOUS MUST EXPERIENCE EVENT. 

~ dj 
founder 

#teremana 
#tequilaofthepeople 
#manamobile 🥃

node.text:
No costar of mine has ever put in harder work ~ with more tenacity, stamina, charm and eloquence than this posh British bird, Emily Blunt. 

As a duo, we’re the hardest workers in the room, speaking to press all day, every day, all around the world 🌍💪🏾

And we also have the most fun….
whilst breaking out the Mana 
🥃😈

Enjoy this video as we happily steer this Disney train right off its rails
🚂💀🤣

Raise em up, you posh bird and mahalo for all the incredible work 🙏🏾🥃

JUNGLE CRUISE finally arrives in theaters worldwide and on Disney+ THIS FRIDAY!!! 

#OffTheRails 
#ItsAJungleDownThere 
#IllDrinkToThat

node.text:
After 3 years in the making, it was with butterflies, with mana and with so much love and gratitude for every soul in the theater that came to celebrate this special moment with us - our official worldwide JUNGLE CRUISE premiere.
It was an incredible experience to share safely alongside the fans, the press and best of all the REAL Disneyland Jungle Cruise skippers right there under the stars at Disneyland.

And very cool to take Emily on her first ever ride of JUNGLE CRUISE 🚢 💀🌴🌍

This one’s for you, Walt…
we hope our film makes your spirit proud! 

Cheers 🥃✨
#JungleCruise

node.text:
For me, that “thing” is a sunrise workout that anchors my day and stacks the cards in my favor to win 🃏 🔑 

An empty room with one cardio machine that faces a bare wall - ain’t looking like much, but you’d be surprised how much noise I’m able to block out and mentally charge up for the day. 

Protect your “thing that allows you to do what you do” and stack that deck in your favor so you can win. 

And thank you to my @Disney partners for having my back by getting me what I need on our big global press junket for JUNGLE CRUISE. 

#protectthething 🔑⚓️☯️
#myladyBertha 💀🖤💦
@zoaenergy💥

My heart is full with gratitude to EVERYONE who shared this momentous WORLD PREMIERE with us at DISNEYLAND!🙏🏾💫🥂

IN 5 DAYS!! 

 #JUNGLECRUISE 
In theaters worldwide & @disneyplus 
THIS FRIDAY 🚢💀🌴🗺🌍🥃

node.text:
I brought the main event MANA MOBILE & @Teremana and Rock Toast, but YOU brought the MANA ENERGY! 

The energy and excitement was electric yesterday at Downtown Disney! We of course had to do a Teremana toast 🥃🥃 to all of you and then Emily decided to offer cocktails and my infamous Rock french toast to everyone all day long - on me - FOR FREE 🤣🥃🍞

Thank you to everyone who came out with their families and friends. You guys are making the MANA MOBILE a MUST EXPERIENCE EVENT! 😊👊🏾

#MANAMOBILE
#NationalTequilaDay
#DowntownDISNEY 
@Teremana

node.text:
Calm before the massive magic ✨

Emily and I quietly chatting (besides the 200 hundred person team members we told to get out of the shot🤣) about how surreal and epic our JUNGLE CRUISE world premiere is going to be tonight at Disneyland! 

In this massive and beautiful outdoor amphitheater, we will have the biggest (and safe) red carpet world premiere of 2021. 

THANK YOU to EVERYONE - all our teams - who have worked tirelessly on creating this magical night 🙏🏾🌟

Countdown is on and we’re just a few hours away….

All aboard! 

#worldpremiere 
#disneyland 
#oldschoolhollywood 
#junglecruise 🚢💀🌴🗺 🥃

node.text:
LOVE the 80’s pro wrestling promo Emily starts with!!
IF YA SMELLLLLL 😂 🎤 👏🏾👏🏾

TONIGHT the dream comes true 🙏🏾✨

Our JUNGLE CRUISE WORLD PREMIERE sets sail tonight from the Happiest Place On Earth:
DISNEYLAND 🌏🌟

In 1955 DISNEYLAND opened its gates to the public for the first time and the JUNGLE CRUISE ride was Walt Disney’s pride & joy. 
* Walt himself was the rides Skipper! 

Tonight’s event is BIG and HISTORIC and Emily and I are HONORED to deliver to this movie to the world. 

Let’s celebrate and have some fun and hopefully Emily’s Dole Whip will stay in her cup 🍨😈

#worldpremiere
#adventureofalifetime 
#junglecruise
#disneyland 
In theaters worldwide & @disneyplus in 6 days!!! 🚢 💀🌴 🌍
